          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-gold">🏆</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="color: var(--slate-900); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.375rem;">15+ Years Experience</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--slate-500); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">Karri McBride brings deep expertise and courthouse relationships across Central Oklahoma.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 flex gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-gold">👩‍💼</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="color: var(--slate-900); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.375rem;">Women-Owned Business</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--slate-500); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">A compassionate, detail-oriented approach to every case we handle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 flex gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-gold">🔒</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="color: var(--slate-900); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.375rem;">Discretion & Confidentiality</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--slate-500); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">Your privacy is our priority. All matters handled with utmost professionalism.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-gold">💳</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="color: var(--slate-900); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.375rem;">Flexible Payment Plans</h3>
